  ## Ranch House Estate
  
  * * *
  
  ### SLEEPS 12 \| 5,500 sq. ft.
  
  Our Ranch House Estate offers the ultimate luxury lodging in Moab, Utah, for groups of friends or family seeking to spend time together in the privacy and comfort of this spacious, inviting retreat. Take in spectacular views overlooking the entire ranch and the meandering Colorado River beyond as you entertain from your outdoor gas grill, private deck, and fully-equipped kitchen.
  
  [Learn More](https://www.sorrelriver.com/accommodations/ranch-house/)
  
