  - ​Flatscreen TV & Wi-Fi
  - ​Kitchenette, mini-fridge,
  
  & coffee maker
  - ​Complimentary bottled water
  
  - ​Sorrel River Ranch bathrobes & slippers
  - ​C.O. Bigelow bath products
  - ​Hairdryer, ironing board, & iron
  - ​Dining Table & chairs
  
