  ## Happy Tails Welcome
  
  * * *
  
  ### Pet Friendly Stays
  
  We know adventures are better when shared with your four-legged friends! That’s why our resort is proudly pet-friendly. Dogs are welcome to join for $75 per night, inclusive of welcome treats, a cozy dog bed, and a water bowl to make them feel right at home. Add our Pet Package during the reservation process or email us at stay@sorrelriver.com. Traveling with your horse? Please inquire at the front desk about our horse boarding options.
  
